────────────────────────`\\n\\n## Changes summary\\n\\n**4 files modified:**\\n\\n| File | Change |\\n|------|--------|\\n| `types.go` | Added 5 IDE types: `kiroIDETranscript`, `kiroIDEHistoryEntry`, `kiroIDEMessage`, `kiroIDEContentBlock`, `kiroIDESessionEntry` |\\n| `transcript.go` | Added dual-format detection (`isCLITranscript`, `tryParseIDETranscript`), IDE→CLI conversion (`convertIDETranscript`, `ideEntryToPaired`), and content extraction helpers (`extractIDEUserText`, `extractIDEAssistantText`) |\\n| `kiro.go` | Added `ideWorkspaceSessionsDir()` for computing IDE workspace paths and `ensureIDETranscript()` for discovering and caching IDE transcripts |\\n| `lifecycle.go` | Wired `ensureIDETranscript()` into the `parseStop()` fallback chain between SQLite and placeholder |\\n\\n**Test coverage**: 9 new tests covering IDE format parsing, prompt/summary extraction, transcript position, format conversion edge cases, and workspace path computation.\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":88,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":104783,\"output_tokens\":473,\"server_tool_use\":{\"web_search_requests\":0,\"web_fetch_requests\":0},\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":88,\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0},\"inference_geo\":\"\",\"iterations\":[],\"speed\":\"standard\"}},\"requestId\":\"req_011CYh5pQ2MPyUC74ywwN95J\",\"type\":\"assistant\",\"uuid\":\"70ded75f-b28b-4559-a870-1684fdd1e6c3\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-04T00:21:22.190Z\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"70ded75f-b28b-4559-a870-1684fdd1e6c3\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/alisha/Projects/wt/kiro-oneshot\",\"sessionId\":\"f6361a7e-c7e7-4190-ac8c-97fe80954831\",\"version\":\"2.1.63\",\"gitBranch\":\"alisha/kiro-oneshot\",\"slug\":\"recursive-giggling-reef\",\"type\":\"progress\",\"data\":{\"type\":\"hook_progress\",\"hookEvent\":\"Stop\",\"hookName\":\"Stop\",\"command\":\"go run ${CL